{"tid":2085730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚德塞：WHO下周派專家赴中調查病毒起源　這非常重要","createTime":"2020-06-30T04:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T07:52:52.000Z","uid":14918,"like":19,"dislike":273,"uniUserReply":151,"replies":[{"pid":"db3dec797cf483b28f1d40d62f59d843b62cea8f","tid":2085730,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"文／中央社日內瓦29日綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）今天在簡報中說，世衛下週將派出一組專家前往中國，調查新型冠狀病毒的起源。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞在線上簡報中說，「了解病毒的起源非常、非常重要」；並說，「我們下週將派遣一組專家前往中國，準備進行調查。我們希望，藉此了解病毒的起源」。"},{"pid":"40ef2a41d071ac8980ecb01bf4b5541a54e42c90","tid":2085730,"uid":166405,"like":212,"dislike":2,"score":210,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"收皮啦唔好下個世紀先去"},{"pid":"548c7076c1558dc960f8b4422629eb31ff2652e6","tid":2085730,"uid":166085,"like":105,"dislike":2,"score":103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"下星期先去？<br />\n陸沉左啦"},{"pid":"539438564e499125c963db495f927a0488ef15e1","tid":2085730,"uid":230104,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔下世？"},{"pid":"c349ff13d3244f679652aa36e1cb0a6a247c4cb4","tid":2085730,"uid":58247,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"新年前爆 依家先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4858480246d705f18d995993616ebb87115e3b56","tid":2085730,"uid":121146,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:14:39.000Z","msg":"下世紀再創傳奇  天謊都等你"},{"pid":"fcb0b61ba4488340187410c7199a7bf95c4799ea","tid":2085730,"uid":230104,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"雙飛+總統套房含食宿套餐已準備好"},{"pid":"06cfc9e246645574adee2fbafdf9ed1cd201adb7","tid":2085730,"uid":82359,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"緊火要叫雞，這很重要"},{"pid":"e11b4d8f57c441fad2489f7de4168e08889b2307","tid":2085730,"u